title: Breaking Down the Tyrese Haliburton Trade, Plus Tyrese Maxey's Game | Upside High
description:
J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks return to break down the news of the Tyrese Haliburton trade to the Indiana Pacers and what might have been behind a move like this (00:24). Plus, they break down the game of Tyrese Maxey of the 76ers and how he can grow in Philadelphia (24:40).
Hosts: J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks
Producer: Steve Ahlman
